Next to Trinity a portal began to open as a blue, red, and white figure fell 
from it and onto his face, burn marks all over his back. He looks over to 
Trinity before his wings cover her and he lays a hand on her stomach. His 
hand begins to glow a bright green as does Trinitys body, her wounds begining 
to heal...

--part1_71.e00dd61.28501e9e_boundary
